Rules

  1. When I say “Class,” you say “Yes?”
  2. Only speak English
    • If you speak Chinese 4 times, I will give you homework :)
  3. Pay attention
  4. Be nice to me and others

If I say a fact, you can say

  • Ohh!
  • Ahh!
  • Wow!
  • Marvelous!
  • Stupendous!
  • Amazing!
  • Wonderful!

Three Types of Question

  • Open Questions
    • Who?
    • What?
    • When?
    • Where?
    • Why?
    • How?
  • Yes/No
  • This/That
